節日生日都唔可以慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3573de25f2a0cf061d3c75ee7f559e0fae06bce","tid":55382,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>異端姐<br />\n好似係叫人犯法先算係邪教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泡菜d變種教會通常都係邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我眼中 異端教會基本同邪教無異"},{"pid":"c64a73db6fcfdebc61e7163ee180b17d5f50cfd1","tid":55382,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇嗰幾個後生女電話？等我拯救佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地有我電話就真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果下次再撞到佢地 呃鳩佢話想聽神嘅話語 但今日就要返工不了 叫佢打電話同你傾 套鳩佢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正佢地都有你電話啦 冇蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f614a4f83ce0948b9509652ab19afd2d6726015f","tid":55382,"uid":29189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁耶和華見證人算唔算邪？<br />\n節日生日都唔可以慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一般基督教教會都被視為異端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耶穌降生算唔算節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0686272cd67f2d0744cdaac2886a89c3f0904b78","tid":55382,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 憑乜話人係邪教<br />\n<br />\n即係非基督教就係邪教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點解基督教又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651d61c2799df71083b764fc5cdae768f713e0f7","tid":55382,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁耶和華見證人算唔算邪？<br />\n節日生日都唔可以慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gi