src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每個星期日朝早上門傳教，比本書仔我叫我睇+讀晒佢指定既篇章出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀完之後問問題，D問題仲要係小學雞都識答(即係問你果段入面XXX做左D咩呀?)，問晒問題後就會派D雜誌比我，記得其中有本叫「警醒」。<br />\nbtw佢地係真係唔比人慶祝生日仲話耶穌唔係釘十字架死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b62030c89e72d3561b1bc5d0f2bd19ad443dfe","tid":55382,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"呢間教會d 女堅正<br />\n食過條勁大波，最少有e<br />\n仲要唔鐘意帶bar, 出街成日飛釘<br />\n<br />\n當初都係因為咁面上當<br />\n食左幾個月之後飛撚左了"},{"pid":"860b09ae8e8f23186832768fa50043ce8efced73","tid":55382,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>扑完啲女先走啦</blockquote><br />\n如果太陽神生日都信<br />\n咁性交轉運都會信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我小學校長0係assembly個時話，係方便d異教徒轉會</blockquote><br />\n好多時吸收異教嘅技倆<br />\n將異教節日習俗吸收<br />\n或者將佢地嘅神降格封聖"},{"pid":"9b4a9dbfa00093008a7c3f873ec41278499c2da1","tid":55382,"uid":6617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"呢間我好似有朋友番緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/qoyclsv7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqoyclsv7&d=FeKzc9hxH25yFSyrpA%2FzUXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7b67c993\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/qoyclsv7</a>"},{"pid":"9eff2bd9cd850e520636e61d60f6353b178af9ac","tid":55382,"uid":66239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4qdmelpv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4qdmelpv&h=2e8102e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><